  "body": "### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n```sh\r\nhelm create bar\r\necho '{{ .Values.bad.doh }}' > bar/templates/foo.yaml\r\nhelm template ./bar/\r\n```\r\n### Expected result\r\nHelm should return error and exist with non-zero exit code, as in previous versions:\r\n```\r\n1 \u2717 (43.5ms) 09:45:19 invidian@dellxps15mateusz /tmp $ ./foo/linux-amd64/helm version\r\nversion.BuildInfo{Version:\"v3.0.3\", GitCommit:\"ac925eb7279f4a6955df663a0128044a8a6b7593\", GitTreeState:\"clean\", GoVersion:\"go1.13.6\"}\r\n0 \u2713 (52.6ms) 09:47:39 invidian@dellxps15mateusz /tmp $ ./foo/linux-amd64/helm template ./bar/\r\nError: template: bar/templates/foo.yaml:1:10: executing \"bar/templates/foo.yaml\" at <.Values.bad.doh>: nil pointer evaluating interface {}.doh\r\n1 \u2717 (52.0ms) 09:47:41 invidian@dellxps15mateusz /tmp $\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Actual output\r\nHelm does not print any warning and exits gracefully:\r\n```\r\n1 \u2717 (52.0ms) 09:47:41 invidian@dellxps15mateusz /tmp $ helm version\r\nversion.BuildInfo{Version:\"v3.1.0\", GitCommit:\"b29d20baf09943e134c2fa5e1e1cab3bf93315fa\", GitTreeState:\"clean\", GoVersion:\"go1.13.7\"}\r\n0 \u2713 (49.1ms) 09:47:53 invidian@dellxps15mateusz /tmp $ helm template ./bar/\r\n\r\n0 \u2713 (49.6ms) 09:47:55 invidian@dellxps15mateusz /tmp $\r\n```\r\n\r\nOutput of `helm version`:\r\n```\r\nversion.BuildInfo{Version:\"v3.1.0\", GitCommit:\"b29d20baf09943e134c2fa5e1e1cab3bf93315fa\", GitTreeState:\"clean\", GoVersion:\"go1.13.7\"}\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n",
